title: Bug 4121 - JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
description: JarExporter causes the system to go out of sync when overwriting the exported jar file in the same directory.
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory, an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time.
EB: The system should not display an out of sync message when overwriting the exported jar file in the same directory.
SR:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Place the exported jar file in the same directory.
3. Overwrite the exported jar file for the second time.
4. Observe the out of sync message.
